Grant Dodwell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grant_Dodwell 0 Grant Radnor Dodwell (born 2 July 1952 in Sydney, New South Wales) is an Australian actor, producer, writer, director, voice artist, and drama teacher. He is a triple recipient of the Silver Logie for Most Popular Actor, he is best known for his roles in television soap opera's including A Country Practice and Home And Away.
